  "description": "More detail about armor in Armor bar!",
  "body": "<h2><strong>Detail Armor Bar</strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The detail armor bar adds more information to the armor bar.</span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br /><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">[This is client-side mod!&nbsp;No need to install on server.]</span><br /></span></h4>\n<h4><strong><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dd0cW3xGEkE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Showcase Video</a></span></strong></h4>\n<h4><strong>Features:</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>Netherite Armor Bar</b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Enchant Protection Type Color Effect</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Armor Mending Effect</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thorns Overlay / Effect</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Armor's Low Durability Warn Effect</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Check out the showcase videos :)</em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4><strong>Protection Colors :&nbsp;</strong></h4>\n<p>- Protection - <span style=\"color: #33cccc;\">Aqua(Cyan)</span></p>\n<p>- Projectile Protection - <span style=\"color: #800080;\">Purple</span></p>\n<p>- Blast Protection - <span style=\"color: #ffff00;\">Yellow</span></p>\n<p>- Fire Protection - <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Red or.. <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Orange</span>?</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>&gt;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/RedLime/DetailArmorBar/wiki/For-Developer-(API-Document)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">API Document</a></h3>",
